1
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,360
Lai Wangshu.

2
00:01:21,440 --> 00:01:22,000
Jiadong,

3
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,800
we've checked two places.

4
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:24,880
Neither address is right.

5
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:26,080
Maybe because of the occupation,

6
00:01:26,080 --> 00:01:27,200
they moved a few times.

7
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,240
That man just said

8
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:29,570
Cai Mingzhi is here.

9
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,130
Let's keep looking.

10
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:32,340
No matter what,

11
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:33,479
we must deliver this remittance letter

12
00:01:33,479 --> 00:01:34,640
to his family.

13
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:36,380
Who are you?

14
00:01:39,039 --> 00:01:40,360
I've been watching you for a while.

15
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,690
Searching door to door.

16
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:42,840
What are you up to?

17
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,320
Sir,

18
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:45,700
we are couriers delivering letters.

19
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:46,960
Liar!

20
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:49,080
These days, people either flee

21
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,240
or become traitors.

22
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,640
Who delivers letters?

23
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:52,970
We really are couriers.

24
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:53,880
It's an urgent family letter

25
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:54,720
from Malaya

26
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:55,920
to their family here.

27
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,660
But the family moved away,

28
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:58,600
so we are searching along the way

29
00:01:58,600 --> 00:01:59,860
for their new address.

30
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,320
Come with us first.

31
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:04,520
We need to do a search.

32
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:05,200
Why?

33
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:06,420
Wangshu, Wangshu.

34
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,360
These two men have guns.

35
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:09,639
And they don't

36
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,919
look like bad guys.

37
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:12,250
Let's just go with them.

38
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:14,680
Move.

39
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,530
Brother Luo.

40
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,690
They really are here to deliver goods.

41
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:30,120
Are you from Malaya?

42
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:35,680
We are from Quanzhou.

43
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:37,240
You two look

44
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,370
like locals too.

45
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,960
Why do you have to search us?

46
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:46,130
There's no harm in telling you.

47
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,130
Look at this.

48
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:55,280
You are from Xiamen's

49
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,560
Futu Blood Soul Society.

50
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,000
Then you are anti-Japanese patriots.

51
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:58,480
We...

52
00:02:59,200 --> 00:02:59,880
Keep it down.

53
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:01,280
We respect you very much.

54
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,000
We are also here on behalf of our compatriots

55
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,320
in Malaya murdered by the Japanese,

56
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,380
to deliver Qiaopi.

57
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,520
The newspaper recently published

58
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,920
that the Japanese in the Malayan tea factory

59
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:11,880
were conducting human experiments.

60
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,960
Did you also bring over the photos and evidence

61
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:15,760
of them murdering Chinese people?

62
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:16,480
Exactly.

63
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,560
Twelve years ago, my parents risked their lives

64
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:20,160
to bring that evidence back,

65
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,890
and died in the tea factory.

66
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,040
Twelve years later,

67
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:24,400
we dealt with the Japanese

68
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,200
and finally got that evidence

69
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:25,760
out,

70
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:27,970
exposing everything to the world.

71
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:30,720
You are the true

72
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:32,360
heroes worthy of admiration.

73
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:32,840
Gangzi.

74
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:34,200
Escort them back quickly,

75
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,320
and help them find the families

76
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:37,250
they need to deliver the Qiaopi to.

77
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,040
Luo.

78
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,560
Don't we still have

79
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,020
intelligence to send out?

80
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:45,520
Can we ask them for help?

81
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,810
I don't think that's appropriate.

82
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:50,640
Just tell us

83
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,040
what you need us to do.

84
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:54,770
To be honest,

85
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:55,800
we do have

86
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:57,440
an important operation tonight.

87
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,160
The two of us came here first

88
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:59,320
to scout.

89
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,130
But now we can't get out.

90
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:02,840
We can't synchronize the details of the operation

91
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,370
with our brothers outside.

92
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:05,650
However,

93
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:08,000
this is a rare opportunity.

94
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,620
It would be a pity to miss tonight.

95
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:11,780
No problem.

96
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:13,080
I saw the Japanese

97
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,320
didn't make things difficult for us just now.

98
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:14,960
If you two

99
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:15,960
trust us,

100
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,399
we can

101
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,680
take the message out.

102
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,320
Thank you so much.

103
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,130
Keep it safe.

104
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:33,600
Okay.

105
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:35,200
Be careful.

106
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:37,120
Whether we can successfully ambush

107
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:37,840
the Japanese and the traitors tonight

108
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:38,900
depends on you two.

109
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,280
Okay, don't worry.

110
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:41,000
We will definitely

111
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,080
deliver the message.

112
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:42,680
You two,

113
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:43,680
take care.

114
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:44,320
Okay.

115
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:50,400
A-Ming,

116
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,640
you will never come back.

117
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:55,800
Thank you.

118
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,640
Thank you

119
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,940
for bringing A-Ming's soul back.

120
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,410
You're welcome.

121
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,560
Thanks.

122
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:03,890
My condolences.

123
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,650
We're heading back now too.

124
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:09,760
Make sure to lock your doors and windows tonight.

125
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:10,520
If you hear any noise,

126
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:11,450
don't be afraid.

127
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:13,720
Okay.

128
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,000
Grandma.

129
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,320
The Japanese will commit violence tonight.

130
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,600
Please stay safe.

131
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:19,840
Okay.

132
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:20,880
Okay.

133
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:21,410
Come.

134
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,640
Hurry back.

135
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,680
Remember to lock your doors and windows.

136
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,280
Okay.

137
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:36,840
Come.

138
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:40,360
I hope the Blood Soul Team

139
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,900
will go smoothly tonight.

140
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,500
They definitely will.

141
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:46,250
Jiadong, let's head back soon too.

142
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:47,290
Let's go.

143
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:55,800
You two must be starving.

144
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,920
Eat some noodles.

145
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,600
Thank you, sister-in-law.

146
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,160
Rest early tonight.

147
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:01,360
Okay.

148
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:05,320
Thank you.

149
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:10,880
Yummy.

150
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:14,280
I heard a couple of days ago

151
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:15,800
that the Blood Soul Group on Kulangsu

152
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:17,960
attacked the Japanese naval commander

153
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,480
and killed a big traitor.

154
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,560
It really scared me.

155
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,120
I was afraid

156
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,850
something would happen to you.

157
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,050
Sister-in-law.

158
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,400
Did the newspaper say

159
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:31,160
if the Blood Soul Group had any casualties?

160
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:31,960
No.

161
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:35,080
They were completely unharmed.

162
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,320
It's really amazing.

163
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:38,360
Great.

164
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:40,280
With these righteous people around,

165
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:41,080
it won't be long before

166
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:42,000
we drive the Japanese

167
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,060
out of our country.

168
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:44,960
I hope so.

169
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:47,280
I'm worried every day.

170
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,010
When you are not at home,

171
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,810
I can't sleep well every night.

172
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:53,000
Sister-in-law.

173
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,730
Has Brother Mingshu been here?

174
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:55,840
No.

175
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:56,800
Brother must have

176
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,130
gone on a mission again.

177
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,980
I don't know how Dad

178
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:01,800
is doing.

179
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,800
I miss him.

180
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,240
Wangshu.

181
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,560
Let's send

182
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,060
a letter of peace tomorrow

183
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:09,920
to tell Dad

184
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:11,080
about our marriage

185
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,400
and the situation here,

186
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:13,080
and also ask about

187
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:14,480
the situation in Malaya.

188
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:18,480
Wangshu, Jiadong.

189
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,480
Something happened to Dad.

190
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,120
What?

191
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,760
What happened to Dad?

192
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:24,920
The overseas remittance from Malaya

193
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,120
says Dad was arrested.

194
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:26,880
What?

195
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:28,610
They are talking nonsense.

196
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,240
Dad has always been cautious

197
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,000
and low-key.

198
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:33,120
How could he incite the Chinese to rebel?

199
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:33,640
And

200
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,840
overthrow the Malayan government?

201
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:37,440
They are just bullshitting.

202
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,650
This remittance letter

203
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,480
was mailed by

204
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:42,420
the Chinese Chamber of Commerce.

205
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,000
It has the seal of the Chamber of Commerce.

206
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,280
The news must be true.

207
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,120
I guess because Yamada and Luowang

208
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,080
didn't catch us,

209
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:50,960
plus the crimes of the Japanese

210
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:52,040
were exposed in the newspaper

211
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,480
and condemned by the whole world,

212
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,480
they were anxious

213
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,880
and wanted to target Dad.

214
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:58,000
It's all my fault

215
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:58,840
for not thinking about

216
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:00,240
Dad's safety in advance.

217
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:02,200
You can't be blamed for this.

218
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:03,440
We never thought of it either.

219
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,680
They are so arrogant.

220
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,960
The chamber of commerce sent a letter.

221
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:08,720
It means Mr. Qin and the others

222
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,920
have no other choice.

223
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:11,060
I didn't expect

224
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:13,160
Yamada's power in Malaya

225
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:15,020
to be greater than before.

226
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:18,360
I don't care how strong and arrogant they are.

227
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,890
I must go save Dad right now.

228
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:20,800
Wangshu,

229
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,170
I'll go with you.

230
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,000
Jiadong.

231
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,360
You can't go.

232
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:28,000
You'd be walking right into a trap.

233
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,080
Will they let you off?

234
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:30,120
Yes, Jiadong.

235
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,300
You'd better stay.

236
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,890
My brother and I will go.

237
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,640
At worst, we'll fight Yamada

238
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:36,039
and that traitor Luo Wang

239
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:37,080
to the bitter end.

240
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,480
Alright.

241
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:40,440
Everyone sit.

242
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,159
Come, sit.

243
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,800
Precisely because I am their target,

244
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:46,920
I must go back.

245
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:47,760
Only then

246
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,160
can I save Dad.

247
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:50,800
Dad and the Chinese Chamber of Commerce

248
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:52,080
are in this passive position

249
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,680
all because of me.

250
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:55,440
I should be the one

251
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,240
to end this.

252
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,690
As for you, Wangshu,

253
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:00,480
you should stay in Quanzhou.

254
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,480
If anything happens to Mingshu

255
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,280
and me,

256
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:05,040
you can stay and help Sister-in-law

257
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,240
take care of the family.

258
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:08,160
Chen Jiadong, what are you talking about?

259
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,240
Do you want to be a hero

260
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,640
and leave me here a widow?

261
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:11,320
No way.

262
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:12,800
We live together,

263
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:13,860
or we die together.

264
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,400
Even in the afterlife, I'll stick with you.

265
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,000
Alright.

266
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,260
Alright, Wangshu.

267
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:17,940
I was wrong.

268
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,240
We'll be together in life and death,

269
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,520
and never part, okay?

270
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:24,080
Why are you suddenly talking about life and death?

271
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,320
If we go, we need to think of a

272
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,250
foolproof plan.

273
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:27,520
Are we going there just to die?

274
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,850
Would Dad agree to that?

275
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,360
Mingshu is right.

276
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:31,600
We need to make a plan.

277
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:32,920
Jiadong,

278
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,300
are you really going back?

279
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:36,690
It's too dangerous.

280
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,530
Sister-in-law.

281
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:41,600
I know.

282
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,680
You and Grandma don't want me

283
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:45,020
to take any more risks.

284
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,280
But Dad was taken

285
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,240
because of me.

286
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,970
So I must go back to save him.

287
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:50,320
I know.

288
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:51,680
Wangshu's dad

289
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:53,000
is also our family.

290
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:55,640
I know I can't stop you.

291
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:59,520
But you must promise me,

292
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:01,340
you'll be careful.

293
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,720
Don't be reckless.

294
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,680
Come back safely,

295
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:05,680
okay?

296
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:06,640
Okay.

297
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,760
